-- Metro to Close Three German Cash & Carry Stores, Combine Wholesale Brands
-- Holger Elfes
-- 2010-06-18T09:00:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/metro-to-close-three-german-cash-carry-stores-combine-wholesale-brands.html

          
          
             Metro AG plans to close three Cash &
Carry stores in Germany by the end of October and sell another,
the company said in a press release today.  
 The company will also combine its two German wholesale
brands as of January, it said. The measures will lead to 900 job
cuts, Metro said.  
          
          


  


        